var book = {
	"name": "Romans",
	"numChapters": 16,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Paul, a servant of Christ Jesus, called to be an apostle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27932A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27932A\"></sup> and set apart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27932B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27932B\"></sup> for the gospel of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27932C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27932C\"></sup>—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>the gospel he promised beforehand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27933D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27933D\"></sup> through his prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27933E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27933E\"></sup> in the Holy Scriptures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27933F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27933F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>regarding his Son, who as to his earthly life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27934G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27934G\"></sup> was a descendant of David,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27934H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27934H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and who through the Spirit of holiness was appointed the Son of God in power<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27935I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27935I\"></sup> by his resurrection from the dead:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27935J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27935J\"></sup> Jesus Christ our Lord.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27935K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27935K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Through him we received grace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27936L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27936L\"></sup> and apostleship to call all the Gentiles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27936M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27936M\"></sup> to the obedience that comes from faith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27936N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27936N\"></sup> for his name’s sake.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And you also are among those Gentiles who are called to belong to Jesus Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27937O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27937O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>To all in Rome who are loved by God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27938P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27938P\"></sup> and called to be his holy people:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27938Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27938Q\"></sup>Grace and peace to you from God our Father and from the Lord Jesus Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27938R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27938R\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>First, I thank my God through Jesus Christ for all of you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27939S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27939S\"></sup> because your faith is being reported all over the world.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27939T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27939T\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>God, whom I serve<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27940U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27940U\"></sup> in my spirit in preaching the gospel of his Son, is my witness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27940V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27940V\"></sup> how constantly I remember you",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>in my prayers at all times;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27941W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27941W\"></sup> and I pray that now at last by God’s will<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27941X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27941X\"></sup> the way may be opened for me to come to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27941Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27941Y\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I long to see you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27942Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27942Z\"></sup> so that I may impart to you some spiritual gift<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27942AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27942AA\"></sup> to make you strong—",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>that is, that you and I may be mutually encouraged by each other’s faith.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I do not want you to be unaware,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27944AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27944AB\"></sup> brothers and sisters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27944AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27944AC\"></sup> that I planned many times to come to you (but have been prevented from doing so until now)<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27944AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27944AD\"></sup> in order that I might have a harvest among you, just as I have had among the other Gentiles.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I am obligated<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27945AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27945AE\"></sup> both to Greeks and non-Greeks, both to the wise and the foolish.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>That is why I am so eager to preach the gospel also to you who are in Rome.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27946AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27946AF\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For I am not ashamed of the gospel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27947AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27947AG\"></sup> because it is the power of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27947AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27947AH\"></sup> that brings salvation to everyone who believes:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27947AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27947AI\"></sup> first to the Jew,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27947AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27947AJ\"></sup> then to the Gentile.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27947AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27947AK\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For in the gospel the righteousness of God is revealed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27948AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27948AL\"></sup>—a righteousness that is by faith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27948AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27948AM\"></sup> from first to last, just as it is written: “The righteous will live by faith.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27948AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27948AN\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The wrath of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27949AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27949AO\"></sup> is being revealed from heaven against all the godlessness and wickedness of people, who suppress the truth by their wickedness,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>since what may be known about God is plain to them, because God has made it plain to them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27950AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27950AP\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For since the creation of the world God’s invisible qualities—his eternal power and divine nature—have been clearly seen, being understood from what has been made,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27951AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27951AQ\"></sup> so that people are without excuse.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27951AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27951AR\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For although they knew God, they neither glorified him as God nor gave thanks to him, but their thinking became futile and their foolish hearts were darkened.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27952AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27952AS\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Although they claimed to be wise, they became fools<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27953AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27953AT\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and exchanged the glory of the immortal God for images<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27954AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27954AU\"></sup> made to look like a mortal human being and birds and animals and reptiles.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore God gave them over<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27955AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27955AV\"></sup> in the sinful desires of their hearts to sexual impurity for the degrading of their bodies with one another.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27955AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27955AW\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>They exchanged the truth about God for a lie,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27956AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27956AX\"></sup> and worshiped and served created things<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27956AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27956AY\"></sup> rather than the Creator—who is forever praised.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27956AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27956AZ\"></sup> Amen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27956BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27956BA\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Because of this, God gave them over<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27957BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27957BB\"></sup> to shameful lusts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27957BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27957BC\"></sup> Even their women exchanged natural sexual relations for unnatural ones.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27957BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27957BD\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>In the same way the men also abandoned natural relations with women and were inflamed with lust for one another. Men committed shameful acts with other men, and received in themselves the due penalty for their error.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27958BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27958BE\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Furthermore, just as they did not think it worthwhile to retain the knowledge of God, so God gave them over<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27959BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27959BF\"></sup> to a depraved mind, so that they do what ought not to be done.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>They have become filled with every kind of wickedness, evil, greed and depravity. They are full of envy, murder, strife, deceit and malice. They are gossips,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27960BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27960BG\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>slanderers, God-haters, insolent, arrogant and boastful; they invent ways of doing evil; they disobey their parents;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27961BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27961BH\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>they have no understanding, no fidelity, no love,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27962BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27962BI\"></sup> no mercy.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Although they know God’s righteous decree that those who do such things deserve death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27963BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27963BJ\"></sup> they not only continue to do these very things but also approve<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27963BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27963BK\"></sup> of those who practice them."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>You, therefore, have no excuse,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27964A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27964A\"></sup> you who pass judgment on someone else, for at whatever point you judge another, you are condemning yourself, because you who pass judgment do the same things.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27964B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27964B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now we know that God’s judgment against those who do such things is based on truth.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So when you, a mere human being, pass judgment on them and yet do the same things, do you think you will escape God’s judgment?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Or do you show contempt for the riches<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27967C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27967C\"></sup> of his kindness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27967D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27967D\"></sup> forbearance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27967E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27967E\"></sup> and patience,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27967F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27967F\"></sup> not realizing that God’s kindness is intended to lead you to repentance?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27967G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27967G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But because of your stubbornness and your unrepentant heart, you are storing up wrath against yourself for the day of God’s wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27968H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27968H\"></sup>, when his righteous judgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27968I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27968I\"></sup> will be revealed.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>God “will repay each person according to what they have done.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27969J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27969J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>To those who by persistence in doing good seek glory, honor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27970K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27970K\"></sup> and immortality,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27970L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27970L\"></sup> he will give eternal life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27970M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27970M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But for those who are self-seeking and who reject the truth and follow evil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27971N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27971N\"></sup> there will be wrath and anger.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27971O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27971O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>There will be trouble and distress for every human being who does evil:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27972P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27972P\"></sup> first for the Jew, then for the Gentile;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27972Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27972Q\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>but glory, honor and peace for everyone who does good: first for the Jew, then for the Gentile.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27973R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27973R\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For God does not show favoritism.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27974S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27974S\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>All who sin apart from the law will also perish apart from the law, and all who sin under the law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27975T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27975T\"></sup> will be judged by the law.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For it is not those who hear the law who are righteous in God’s sight, but it is those who obey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27976U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27976U\"></sup> the law who will be declared righteous.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>(Indeed, when Gentiles, who do not have the law, do by nature things required by the law,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27977V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27977V\"></sup> they are a law for themselves, even though they do not have the law.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>They show that the requirements of the law are written on their hearts, their consciences also bearing witness, and their thoughts sometimes accusing them and at other times even defending them.)",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>This will take place on the day when God judges people’s secrets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27979W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27979W\"></sup> through Jesus Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27979X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27979X\"></sup> as my gospel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27979Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27979Y\"></sup> declares.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now you, if you call yourself a Jew; if you rely on the law and boast in God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27980Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27980Z\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>if you know his will and approve of what is superior because you are instructed by the law;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>if you are convinced that you are a guide for the blind, a light for those who are in the dark,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>an instructor of the foolish, a teacher of little children, because you have in the law the embodiment of knowledge and truth—",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>you, then, who teach others, do you not teach yourself? You who preach against stealing, do you steal?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27984AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27984AA\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>You who say that people should not commit adultery, do you commit adultery? You who abhor idols, do you rob temples?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27985AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27985AB\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>You who boast in the law,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27986AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27986AC\"></sup> do you dishonor God by breaking the law?",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>As it is written: “God’s name is blasphemed among the Gentiles because of you.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27987AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27987AD\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Circumcision has value if you observe the law,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27988AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27988AE\"></sup> but if you break the law, you have become as though you had not been circumcised.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27988AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27988AF\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>So then, if those who are not circumcised keep the law’s requirements,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27989AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27989AG\"></sup> will they not be regarded as though they were circumcised?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27989AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27989AH\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The one who is not circumcised physically and yet obeys the law will condemn you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27990AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27990AI\"></sup> who, even though you have the written code and circumcision, are a lawbreaker.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>A person is not a Jew who is one only outwardly,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27991AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27991AJ\"></sup> nor is circumcision merely outward and physical.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27991AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27991AK\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>No, a person is a Jew who is one inwardly; and circumcision is circumcision of the heart,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27992AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27992AL\"></sup> by the Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27992AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27992AM\"></sup> not by the written code.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27992AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27992AN\"></sup> Such a person’s praise is not from other people, but from God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27992AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27992AO\"></sup>"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>What advantage, then, is there in being a Jew, or what value is there in circumcision?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Much in every way!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27994A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27994A\"></sup> First of all, the Jews have been entrusted with the very words of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27994B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27994B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>What if some were unfaithful?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27995C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27995C\"></sup> Will their unfaithfulness nullify God’s faithfulness?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27995D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27995D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Not at all! Let God be true,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27996E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27996E\"></sup> and every human being a liar.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27996F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27996F\"></sup> As it is written:“So that you may be proved right when you speakand prevail when you judge.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27996G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27996G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But if our unrighteousness brings out God’s righteousness more clearly,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27997H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27997H\"></sup> what shall we say? That God is unjust in bringing his wrath on us? (I am using a human argument.)<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27997I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27997I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Certainly not! If that were so, how could God judge the world?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27998J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27998J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Someone might argue, “If my falsehood enhances God’s truthfulness and so increases his glory,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27999K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27999K\"></sup> why am I still condemned as a sinner?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-27999L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-27999L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Why not say—as some slanderously claim that we say—“Let us do evil that good may result”?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28000M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28000M\"></sup> Their condemnation is just!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>What shall we conclude then? Do we have any advantage?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28001N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28001N\"></sup> Not at all! For we have already made the charge that Jews and Gentiles alike are all under the power of sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28001O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28001O\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>As it is written:“There is no one righteous, not even one;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>there is no one who understands;there is no one who seeks God.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>All have turned away,they have together become worthless;there is no one who does good,not even one.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28004P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28004P\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Their throats are open graves;their tongues practice deceit.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28005Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28005Q\"></sup>“The poison of vipers is on their lips.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28005R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28005R\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>“Their mouths are full of cursing and bitterness.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28006S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28006S\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Their feet are swift to shed blood;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>ruin and misery mark their ways,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>and the way of peace they do not know.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28009T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28009T\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>“There is no fear of God before their eyes.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28010U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28010U\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Now we know that whatever the law says,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28011V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28011V\"></sup> it says to those who are under the law,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28011W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28011W\"></sup> so that every mouth may be silenced<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28011X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28011X\"></sup> and the whole world held accountable to God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28011Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28011Y\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Therefore no one will be declared righteous in God’s sight by the works of the law;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28012Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28012Z\"></sup> rather, through the law we become conscious of our sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28012AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28012AA\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But now apart from the law the righteousness of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28013AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28013AB\"></sup> has been made known, to which the Law and the Prophets testify.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28013AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28013AC\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>This righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28014AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28014AD\"></sup> is given through faith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28014AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28014AE\"></sup> in Jesus Christ<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28014AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28014AF\"></sup> to all who believe.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28014AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28014AG\"></sup> There is no difference between Jew and Gentile,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28014AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28014AH\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>for all have sinned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28015AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28015AI\"></sup> and fall short of the glory of God,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>and all are justified<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28016AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28016AJ\"></sup> freely by his grace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28016AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28016AK\"></sup> through the redemption<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28016AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28016AL\"></sup> that came by Christ Jesus.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>God presented Christ as a sacrifice of atonement,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28017AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28017AM\"></sup> through the shedding of his blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28017AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28017AN\"></sup>—to be received by faith. He did this to demonstrate his righteousness, because in his forbearance he had left the sins committed beforehand unpunished<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28017AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28017AO\"></sup>—",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>he did it to demonstrate his righteousness at the present time, so as to be just and the one who justifies those who have faith in Jesus.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Where, then, is boasting?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28019AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28019AP\"></sup> It is excluded. Because of what law? The law that requires works? No, because of the law that requires faith.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>For we maintain that a person is justified by faith apart from the works of the law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28020AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28020AQ\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Or is God the God of Jews only? Is he not the God of Gentiles too? Yes, of Gentiles too,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28021AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28021AR\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>since there is only one God, who will justify the circumcised by faith and the uncircumcised through that same faith.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28022AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28022AS\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Do we, then, nullify the law by this faith? Not at all! Rather, we uphold the law."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>What then shall we say<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28024A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28024A\"></sup> that Abraham, our forefather according to the flesh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28024B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28024B\"></sup> discovered in this matter?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>If, in fact, Abraham was justified by works, he had something to boast about—but not before God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28025C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28025C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>What does Scripture say? “Abraham believed God, and it was credited to him as righteousness.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28026D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28026D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now to the one who works, wages are not credited as a gift<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28027E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28027E\"></sup> but as an obligation.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>However, to the one who does not work but trusts God who justifies the ungodly, their faith is credited as righteousness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28028F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28028F\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>David says the same thing when he speaks of the blessedness of the one to whom God credits righteousness apart from works:",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Blessed are thosewhose transgressions are forgiven,whose sins are covered.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Blessed is the onewhose sin the Lord will never count against them.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28031G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28031G\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Is this blessedness only for the circumcised, or also for the uncircumcised?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28032H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28032H\"></sup> We have been saying that Abraham’s faith was credited to him as righteousness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28032I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28032I\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Under what circumstances was it credited? Was it after he was circumcised, or before? It was not after, but before!",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And he received circumcision as a sign, a seal of the righteousness that he had by faith while he was still uncircumcised.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28034J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28034J\"></sup> So then, he is the father<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28034K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28034K\"></sup> of all who believe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28034L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28034L\"></sup> but have not been circumcised, in order that righteousness might be credited to them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And he is then also the father of the circumcised who not only are circumcised but who also follow in the footsteps of the faith that our father Abraham had before he was circumcised.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>It was not through the law that Abraham and his offspring received the promise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28036M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28036M\"></sup> that he would be heir of the world,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28036N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28036N\"></sup> but through the righteousness that comes by faith.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28036O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28036O\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For if those who depend on the law are heirs, faith means nothing and the promise is worthless,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28037P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28037P\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>because the law brings wrath.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28038Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28038Q\"></sup> And where there is no law there is no transgression.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28038R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28038R\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore, the promise comes by faith, so that it may be by grace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28039S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28039S\"></sup> and may be guaranteed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28039T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28039T\"></sup> to all Abraham’s offspring—not only to those who are of the law but also to those who have the faith of Abraham. He is the father of us all.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28039U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28039U\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>As it is written: “I have made you a father of many nations.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28040V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28040V\"></sup> He is our father in the sight of God, in whom he believed—the God who gives life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28040W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28040W\"></sup> to the dead and calls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28040X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28040X\"></sup> into being things that were not.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28040Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28040Y\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Against all hope, Abraham in hope believed and so became the father of many nations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28041Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28041Z\"></sup> just as it had been said to him, “So shall your offspring be.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28041AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28041AA\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Without weakening in his faith, he faced the fact that his body was as good as dead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28042AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28042AB\"></sup>—since he was about a hundred years old<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28042AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28042AC\"></sup>—and that Sarah’s womb was also dead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28042AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28042AD\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Yet he did not waver through unbelief regarding the promise of God, but was strengthened<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28043AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28043AE\"></sup> in his faith and gave glory to God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28043AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28043AF\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>being fully persuaded that God had power to do what he had promised.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28044AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28044AG\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>This is why “it was credited to him as righteousness.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28045AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28045AH\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The words “it was credited to him” were written not for him alone,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>but also for us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28047AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28047AI\"></sup> to whom God will credit righteousness—for us who believe in him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28047AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28047AJ\"></sup> who raised Jesus our Lord from the dead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28047AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28047AK\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>He was delivered over to death for our sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28048AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28048AL\"></sup> and was raised to life for our justification.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28048AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28048AM\"></sup>"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>Therefore, since we have been justified<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28049A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28049A\"></sup> through faith,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28049B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28049B\"></sup> we have peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28049C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28049C\"></sup> with God through our Lord Jesus Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28049D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28049D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>through whom we have gained access<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28050E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28050E\"></sup> by faith into this grace in which we now stand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28050F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28050F\"></sup> And we boast in the hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28050G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28050G\"></sup> of the glory of God.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Not only so, but we also glory in our sufferings,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28051H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28051H\"></sup> because we know that suffering produces perseverance;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28051I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28051I\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>perseverance, character; and character, hope.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28053J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28053J\"></sup> does not put us to shame, because God’s love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28053K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28053K\"></sup> has been poured out into our hearts through the Holy Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28053L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28053L\"></sup> who has been given to us.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>You see, at just the right time,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28054M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28054M\"></sup> when we were still powerless,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28054N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28054N\"></sup> Christ died for the ungodly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28054O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28054O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Very rarely will anyone die for a righteous person, though for a good person someone might possibly dare to die.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But God demonstrates his own love for us in this: While we were still sinners, Christ died for us.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28056P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28056P\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Since we have now been justified<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28057Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28057Q\"></sup> by his blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28057R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28057R\"></sup> how much more shall we be saved from God’s wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28057S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28057S\"></sup> through him!",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For if, while we were God’s enemies,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28058T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28058T\"></sup> we were reconciled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28058U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28058U\"></sup> to him through the death of his Son, how much more, having been reconciled, shall we be saved through his life!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28058V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28058V\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Not only is this so, but we also boast in God through our Lord Jesus Christ, through whom we have now received reconciliation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28059W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28059W\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore, just as sin entered the world through one man,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28060X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28060X\"></sup> and death through sin,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28060Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28060Y\"></sup> and in this way death came to all people, because all sinned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28060Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28060Z\"></sup>—",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>To be sure, sin was in the world before the law was given, but sin is not charged against anyone’s account where there is no law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28061AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28061AA\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Nevertheless, death reigned from the time of Adam to the time of Moses, even over those who did not sin by breaking a command, as did Adam,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28062AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28062AB\"></sup> who is a pattern of the one to come.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28062AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28062AC\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But the gift is not like the trespass. For if the many died by the trespass of the one man,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28063AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28063AD\"></sup> how much more did God’s grace and the gift that came by the grace of the one man, Jesus Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28063AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28063AE\"></sup> overflow to the many!",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Nor can the gift of God be compared with the result of one man’s sin: The judgment followed one sin and brought condemnation, but the gift followed many trespasses and brought justification.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For if, by the trespass of the one man, death<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28065AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28065AF\"></sup> reigned through that one man, how much more will those who receive God’s abundant provision of grace and of the gift of righteousness reign in life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28065AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28065AG\"></sup> through the one man, Jesus Christ!",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Consequently, just as one trespass resulted in condemnation for all people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28066AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28066AH\"></sup> so also one righteous act resulted in justification<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28066AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28066AI\"></sup> and life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28066AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28066AJ\"></sup> for all people.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For just as through the disobedience of the one man<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28067AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28067AK\"></sup> the many were made sinners,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28067AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28067AL\"></sup> so also through the obedience<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28067AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28067AM\"></sup> of the one man the many will be made righteous.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The law was brought in so that the trespass might increase.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28068AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28068AN\"></sup> But where sin increased, grace increased all the more,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28068AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28068AO\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>so that, just as sin reigned in death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28069AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28069AP\"></sup> so also grace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28069AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28069AQ\"></sup> might reign through righteousness to bring eternal life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28069AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28069AR\"></sup> through Jesus Christ our Lord."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>What shall we say, then?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28070A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28070A\"></sup> Shall we go on sinning so that grace may increase?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28070B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28070B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>By no means! We are those who have died to sin;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28071C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28071C\"></sup> how can we live in it any longer?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Or don’t you know that all of us who were baptized<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28072D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28072D\"></sup> into Christ Jesus were baptized into his death?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>We were therefore buried with him through baptism into death<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28073E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28073E\"></sup> in order that, just as Christ was raised from the dead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28073F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28073F\"></sup> through the glory of the Father, we too may live a new life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28073G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28073G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For if we have been united with him in a death like his, we will certainly also be united with him in a resurrection like his.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28074H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28074H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For we know that our old self<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28075I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28075I\"></sup> was crucified with him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28075J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28075J\"></sup> so that the body ruled by sin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28075K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28075K\"></sup> might be done away with, that we should no longer be slaves to sin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28075L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28075L\"></sup>—",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>because anyone who has died has been set free from sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28076M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28076M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Now if we died with Christ, we believe that we will also live with him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28077N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28077N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For we know that since Christ was raised from the dead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28078O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28078O\"></sup> he cannot die again; death no longer has mastery over him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28078P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28078P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The death he died, he died to sin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28079Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28079Q\"></sup> once for all;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28079R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28079R\"></sup> but the life he lives, he lives to God.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>In the same way, count yourselves dead to sin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28080S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28080S\"></sup> but alive to God in Christ Jesus.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore do not let sin reign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28081T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28081T\"></sup> in your mortal body so that you obey its evil desires.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Do not offer any part of yourself to sin as an instrument of wickedness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28082U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28082U\"></sup> but rather offer yourselves to God as those who have been brought from death to life; and offer every part of yourself to him as an instrument of righteousness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28082V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28082V\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For sin shall no longer be your master,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28083W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28083W\"></sup> because you are not under the law,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28083X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28083X\"></sup> but under grace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28083Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28083Y\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>What then? Shall we sin because we are not under the law but under grace?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28084Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28084Z\"></sup> By no means!",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Don’t you know that when you offer yourselves to someone as obedient slaves, you are slaves of the one you obey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28085AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28085AA\"></sup>—whether you are slaves to sin,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28085AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28085AB\"></sup> which leads to death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28085AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28085AC\"></sup> or to obedience, which leads to righteousness?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But thanks be to God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28086AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28086AD\"></sup> that, though you used to be slaves to sin,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28086AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28086AE\"></sup> you have come to obey from your heart the pattern of teaching<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28086AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28086AF\"></sup> that has now claimed your allegiance.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>You have been set free from sin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28087AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28087AG\"></sup> and have become slaves to righteousness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28087AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28087AH\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I am using an example from everyday life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28088AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28088AI\"></sup> because of your human limitations. Just as you used to offer yourselves as slaves to impurity and to ever-increasing wickedness, so now offer yourselves as slaves to righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28088AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28088AJ\"></sup> leading to holiness.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>When you were slaves to sin,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28089AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28089AK\"></sup> you were free from the control of righteousness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28089AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28089AL\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>What benefit did you reap at that time from the things you are now ashamed of? Those things result in death!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28090AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28090AM\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But now that you have been set free from sin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28091AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28091AN\"></sup> and have become slaves of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28091AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28091AO\"></sup> the benefit you reap leads to holiness, and the result is eternal life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28091AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28091AP\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For the wages of sin is death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28092AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28092AQ\"></sup> but the gift of God is eternal life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28092AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28092AR\"></sup> in Christ Jesus our Lord."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>Do you not know, brothers and sisters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28093A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28093A\"></sup>—for I am speaking to those who know the law—that the law has authority over someone only as long as that person lives?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For example, by law a married woman is bound to her husband as long as he is alive, but if her husband dies, she is released from the law that binds her to him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28094B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28094B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So then, if she has sexual relations with another man while her husband is still alive, she is called an adulteress.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28095C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28095C\"></sup> But if her husband dies, she is released from that law and is not an adulteress if she marries another man.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So, my brothers and sisters, you also died to the law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28096D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28096D\"></sup> through the body of Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28096E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28096E\"></sup> that you might belong to another,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28096F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28096F\"></sup> to him who was raised from the dead, in order that we might bear fruit for God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For when we were in the realm of the flesh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28097G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28097G\"></sup> the sinful passions aroused by the law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28097H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28097H\"></sup> were at work in us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28097I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28097I\"></sup> so that we bore fruit for death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28097J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28097J\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But now, by dying to what once bound us, we have been released from the law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28098K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28098K\"></sup> so that we serve in the new way of the Spirit, and not in the old way of the written code.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28098L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28098L\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>What shall we say, then?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28099M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28099M\"></sup> Is the law sinful? Certainly not!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28099N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28099N\"></sup> Nevertheless, I would not have known what sin was had it not been for the law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28099O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28099O\"></sup> For I would not have known what coveting really was if the law had not said, “You shall not covet.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28099P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28099P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But sin, seizing the opportunity afforded by the commandment,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28100Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28100Q\"></sup> produced in me every kind of coveting. For apart from the law, sin was dead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28100R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28100R\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Once I was alive apart from the law; but when the commandment came, sin sprang to life and I died.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I found that the very commandment that was intended to bring life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28102S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28102S\"></sup> actually brought death.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For sin, seizing the opportunity afforded by the commandment,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28103T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28103T\"></sup> deceived me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28103U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28103U\"></sup> and through the commandment put me to death.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So then, the law is holy, and the commandment is holy, righteous and good.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28104V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28104V\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Did that which is good, then, become death to me? By no means! Nevertheless, in order that sin might be recognized as sin, it used what is good<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28105W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28105W\"></sup> to bring about my death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28105X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28105X\"></sup> so that through the commandment sin might become utterly sinful.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>We know that the law is spiritual; but I am unspiritual,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28106Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28106Y\"></sup> sold<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28106Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28106Z\"></sup> as a slave to sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28106AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28106AA\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I do not understand what I do. For what I want to do I do not do, but what I hate I do.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28107AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28107AB\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And if I do what I do not want to do, I agree that the law is good.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28108AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28108AC\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>As it is, it is no longer I myself who do it, but it is sin living in me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28109AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28109AD\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For I know that good itself does not dwell in me, that is, in my sinful nature.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28110AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28110AE\"></sup> For I have the desire to do what is good, but I cannot carry it out.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For I do not do the good I want to do, but the evil I do not want to do—this I keep on doing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28111AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28111AF\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now if I do what I do not want to do, it is no longer I who do it, but it is sin living in me that does it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28112AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28112AG\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So I find this law at work:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28113AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28113AH\"></sup> Although I want to do good, evil is right there with me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For in my inner being<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28114AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28114AI\"></sup> I delight in God’s law;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28114AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28114AJ\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>but I see another law at work in me, waging war<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28115AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28115AK\"></sup> against the law of my mind and making me a prisoner of the law of sin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28115AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28115AL\"></sup> at work within me.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>What a wretched man I am! Who will rescue me from this body that is subject to death?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28116AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28116AM\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Thanks be to God, who delivers me through Jesus Christ our Lord!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28117AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28117AN\"></sup>So then, I myself in my mind am a slave to God’s law,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28117AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28117AO\"></sup> but in my sinful nature a slave to the law of sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28117AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28117AP\"></sup>"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Therefore, there is now no condemnation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28118A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28118A\"></sup> for those who are in Christ Jesus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28118B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28118B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>because through Christ Jesus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28119C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28119C\"></sup> the law of the Spirit who gives life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28119D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28119D\"></sup> has set you free<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28119E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28119E\"></sup> from the law of sin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28119F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28119F\"></sup> and death.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For what the law was powerless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28120G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28120G\"></sup> to do because it was weakened by the flesh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28120H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28120H\"></sup> God did by sending his own Son in the likeness of sinful flesh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28120I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28120I\"></sup> to be a sin offering.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28120J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28120J\"></sup> And so he condemned sin in the flesh,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>in order that the righteous requirement<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28121K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28121K\"></sup> of the law might be fully met in us, who do not live according to the flesh but according to the Spirit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28121L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28121L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Those who live according to the flesh have their minds set on what the flesh desires;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28122M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28122M\"></sup> but those who live in accordance with the Spirit have their minds set on what the Spirit desires.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28122N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28122N\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The mind governed by the flesh is death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28123O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28123O\"></sup> but the mind governed by the Spirit is life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28123P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28123P\"></sup> and peace.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The mind governed by the flesh is hostile to God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28124Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28124Q\"></sup> it does not submit to God’s law, nor can it do so.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Those who are in the realm of the flesh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28125R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28125R\"></sup> cannot please God.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You, however, are not in the realm of the flesh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28126S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28126S\"></sup> but are in the realm of the Spirit, if indeed the Spirit of God lives in you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28126T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28126T\"></sup> And if anyone does not have the Spirit of Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28126U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28126U\"></sup> they do not belong to Christ.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But if Christ is in you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28127V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28127V\"></sup> then even though your body is subject to death because of sin, the Spirit gives life because of righteousness.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And if the Spirit of him who raised Jesus from the dead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28128W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28128W\"></sup> is living in you, he who raised Christ from the dead will also give life to your mortal bodies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28128X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28128X\"></sup> because of his Spirit who lives in you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore, brothers and sisters, we have an obligation—but it is not to the flesh, to live according to it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28129Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28129Y\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For if you live according to the flesh, you will die;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28130Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28130Z\"></sup> but if by the Spirit you put to death the misdeeds of the body,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28130AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28130AA\"></sup> you will live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28130AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28130AB\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For those who are led by the Spirit of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28131AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28131AC\"></sup> are the children of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28131AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28131AD\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28132AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28132AE\"></sup> you received does not make you slaves, so that you live in fear again;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28132AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28132AF\"></sup> rather, the Spirit you received brought about your adoption to sonship. And by him we cry, <i>“Abba,</i> Father.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28132AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28132AG\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The Spirit himself testifies with our spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28133AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28133AH\"></sup> that we are God’s children.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28133AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28133AI\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now if we are children, then we are heirs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28134AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28134AJ\"></sup>—heirs of God and co-heirs with Christ, if indeed we share in his sufferings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28134AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28134AK\"></sup> in order that we may also share in his glory.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28134AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28134AL\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I consider that our present sufferings are not worth comparing with the glory that will be revealed in us.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28135AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28135AM\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For the creation waits in eager expectation for the children of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28136AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28136AN\"></sup> to be revealed.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For the creation was subjected to frustration, not by its own choice, but by the will of the one who subjected it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28137AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28137AO\"></sup> in hope",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>that the creation itself will be liberated from its bondage to decay<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28138AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28138AP\"></sup> and brought into the freedom and glory of the children of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28138AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28138AQ\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>We know that the whole creation has been groaning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28139AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28139AR\"></sup> as in the pains of childbirth right up to the present time.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Not only so, but we ourselves, who have the firstfruits of the Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28140AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28140AS\"></sup> groan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28140AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28140AT\"></sup> inwardly as we wait eagerly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28140AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28140AU\"></sup> for our adoption to sonship, the redemption of our bodies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28140AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28140AV\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For in this hope we were saved.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28141AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28141AW\"></sup> But hope that is seen is no hope at all.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28141AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28141AX\"></sup> Who hopes for what they already have?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But if we hope for what we do not yet have, we wait for it patiently.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28142AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28142AY\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>In the same way, the Spirit helps us in our weakness. We do not know what we ought to pray for, but the Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28143AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28143AZ\"></sup> himself intercedes for us<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28143BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28143BA\"></sup> through wordless groans.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And he who searches our hearts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28144BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28144BB\"></sup> knows the mind of the Spirit, because the Spirit intercedes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28144BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28144BC\"></sup> for God’s people in accordance with the will of God.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And we know that in all things God works for the good<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28145BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28145BD\"></sup> of those who love him, who have been called<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28145BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28145BE\"></sup> according to his purpose.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28145BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28145BF\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>For those God foreknew<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28146BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28146BG\"></sup> he also predestined<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28146BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28146BH\"></sup> to be conformed to the image of his Son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28146BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28146BI\"></sup> that he might be the firstborn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28146BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28146BJ\"></sup> among many brothers and sisters.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And those he predestined,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28147BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28147BK\"></sup> he also called;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28147BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28147BL\"></sup> those he called, he also justified;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28147BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28147BM\"></sup> those he justified, he also glorified.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28147BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28147BN\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>What, then, shall we say in response to these things?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28148BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28148BO\"></sup> If God is for us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28148BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28148BP\"></sup> who can be against us?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28148BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28148BQ\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>He who did not spare his own Son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28149BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28149BR\"></sup> but gave him up for us all—how will he not also, along with him, graciously give us all things?",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Who will bring any charge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28150BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28150BS\"></sup> against those whom God has chosen? It is God who justifies.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Who then is the one who condemns?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28151BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28151BT\"></sup> No one. Christ Jesus who died<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28151BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28151BU\"></sup>—more than that, who was raised to life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28151BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28151BV\"></sup>—is at the right hand of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28151BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28151BW\"></sup> and is also interceding for us.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28151BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28151BX\"></sup>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Who shall separate us from the love of Christ?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28152BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28152BY\"></sup> Shall trouble or hardship or persecution or famine or nakedness or danger or sword?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28152BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28152BZ\"></sup>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>As it is written:“For your sake we face death all day long;we are considered as sheep to be slaughtered.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28153CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28153CA\"></sup>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>No, in all these things we are more than conquerors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28154CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28154CB\"></sup> through him who loved us.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28154CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28154CC\"></sup>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>For I am convinced that neither death nor life, neither angels nor demons, neither the present nor the future,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28155CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28155CD\"></sup> nor any powers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28155CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28155CE\"></sup>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>neither height nor depth, nor anything else in all creation, will be able to separate us from the love of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28156CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28156CF\"></sup> that is in Christ Jesus our Lord.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28156CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28156CG\"></sup>"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>I speak the truth in Christ—I am not lying,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28157A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28157A\"></sup> my conscience confirms<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28157B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28157B\"></sup> it through the Holy Spirit—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I have great sorrow and unceasing anguish in my heart.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For I could wish that I myself<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28159C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28159C\"></sup> were cursed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28159D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28159D\"></sup> and cut off from Christ for the sake of my people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28159E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28159E\"></sup> those of my own race,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28159F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28159F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>the people of Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28160G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28160G\"></sup> Theirs is the adoption to sonship;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28160H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28160H\"></sup> theirs the divine glory,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28160I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28160I\"></sup> the covenants,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28160J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28160J\"></sup> the receiving of the law,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28160K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28160K\"></sup> the temple worship<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28160L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28160L\"></sup> and the promises.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28160M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28160M\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Theirs are the patriarchs,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28161N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28161N\"></sup> and from them is traced the human ancestry of the Messiah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28161O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28161O\"></sup> who is God over all,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28161P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28161P\"></sup> forever praised!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28161Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28161Q\"></sup> Amen.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>It is not as though God’s word<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28162R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28162R\"></sup> had failed. For not all who are descended from Israel are Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28162S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28162S\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Nor because they are his descendants are they all Abraham’s children. On the contrary, “It is through Isaac that your offspring will be reckoned.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28163T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28163T\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>In other words, it is not the children by physical descent who are God’s children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28164U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28164U\"></sup> but it is the children of the promise who are regarded as Abraham’s offspring.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28164V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28164V\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For this was how the promise was stated: “At the appointed time I will return, and Sarah will have a son.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28165W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28165W\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Not only that, but Rebekah’s children were conceived at the same time by our father Isaac.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28166X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28166X\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Yet, before the twins were born or had done anything good or bad<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28167Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28167Y\"></sup>—in order that God’s purpose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28167Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28167Z\"></sup> in election might stand:",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>not by works but by him who calls—she was told, “The older will serve the younger.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28168AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28168AA\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Just as it is written: “Jacob I loved, but Esau I hated.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28169AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28169AB\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>What then shall we say?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28170AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28170AC\"></sup> Is God unjust? Not at all!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28170AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28170AD\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For he says to Moses,“I will have mercy on whom I have mercy,and I will have compassion on whom I have compassion.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28171AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28171AE\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>It does not, therefore, depend on human desire or effort, but on God’s mercy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28172AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28172AF\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For Scripture says to Pharaoh: “I raised you up for this very purpose, that I might display my power in you and that my name might be proclaimed in all the earth.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28173AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28173AG\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Therefore God has mercy on whom he wants to have mercy, and he hardens whom he wants to harden.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28174AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28174AH\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>One of you will say to me:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28175AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28175AI\"></sup> “Then why does God still blame us?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28175AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28175AJ\"></sup> For who is able to resist his will?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28175AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28175AK\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But who are you, a human being, to talk back to God?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28176AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28176AL\"></sup> “Shall what is formed say to the one who formed it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28176AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28176AM\"></sup> ‘Why did you make me like this?’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28176AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28176AN\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Does not the potter have the right to make out of the same lump of clay some pottery for special purposes and some for common use?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28177AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28177AO\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>What if God, although choosing to show his wrath and make his power known, bore with great patience<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28178AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28178AP\"></sup> the objects of his wrath—prepared for destruction?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28178AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28178AQ\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>What if he did this to make the riches of his glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28179AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28179AR\"></sup> known to the objects of his mercy, whom he prepared in advance for glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28179AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28179AS\"></sup>—",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>even us, whom he also called,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28180AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28180AT\"></sup> not only from the Jews but also from the Gentiles?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28180AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28180AU\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>As he says in Hosea:“I will call them ‘my people’ who are not my people;and I will call her ‘my loved one’ who is not my loved one,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28181AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28181AV\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and,“In the very place where it was said to them,‘You are not my people,’there they will be called ‘children of the living God.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28182AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28182AW\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Isaiah cries out concerning Israel:“Though the number of the Israelites be like the sand by the sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28183AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28183AX\"></sup>only the remnant will be saved.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28183AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28183AY\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>For the Lord will carry outhis sentence on earth with speed and finality.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28184AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28184AZ\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>It is just as Isaiah said previously:“Unless the Lord Almighty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28185BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28185BA\"></sup>had left us descendants,we would have become like Sodom,we would have been like Gomorrah.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28185BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28185BB\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>What then shall we say?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28186BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28186BC\"></sup> That the Gentiles, who did not pursue righteousness, have obtained it, a righteousness that is by faith;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28186BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28186BD\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>but the people of Israel, who pursued the law as the way of righteousness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28187BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28187BE\"></sup> have not attained their goal.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28187BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28187BF\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Why not? Because they pursued it not by faith but as if it were by works. They stumbled over the stumbling stone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28188BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28188BG\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>As it is written:“See, I lay in Zion a stone that causes people to stumbleand a rock that makes them fall,and the one who believes in him will never be put to shame.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28189BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28189BH\"></sup>"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Brothers and sisters, my heart’s desire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28190A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28190A\"></sup> and prayer to God for the Israelites is that they may be saved.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For I can testify about them that they are zealous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28191B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28191B\"></sup> for God, but their zeal is not based on knowledge.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Since they did not know the righteousness of God and sought to establish their own, they did not submit to God’s righteousness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28192C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28192C\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Christ is the culmination of the law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28193D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28193D\"></sup> so that there may be righteousness for everyone who believes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28193E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28193E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Moses writes this about the righteousness that is by the law: “The person who does these things will live by them.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28194F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28194F\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But the righteousness that is by faith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28195G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28195G\"></sup> says: “Do not say in your heart, ‘Who will ascend into heaven?’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28195H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28195H\"></sup> (that is, to bring Christ down)",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“or ‘Who will descend into the deep?’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28196I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28196I\"></sup> (that is, to bring Christ up from the dead).<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28196J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28196J\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But what does it say? “The word is near you; it is in your mouth and in your heart,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28197K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28197K\"></sup> that is, the message concerning faith that we proclaim:",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>If you declare<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28198L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28198L\"></sup> with your mouth, “Jesus is Lord,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28198M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28198M\"></sup> and believe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28198N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28198N\"></sup> in your heart that God raised him from the dead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28198O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28198O\"></sup> you will be saved.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28198P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28198P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For it is with your heart that you believe and are justified, and it is with your mouth that you profess your faith and are saved.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>As Scripture says, “Anyone who believes in him will never be put to shame.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28200Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28200Q\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For there is no difference between Jew and Gentile<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28201R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28201R\"></sup>—the same Lord is Lord of all<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28201S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28201S\"></sup> and richly blesses all who call on him,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>for, “Everyone who calls on the name of the Lord<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28202T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28202T\"></sup> will be saved.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28202U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28202U\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>How, then, can they call on the one they have not believed in? And how can they believe in the one of whom they have not heard? And how can they hear without someone preaching to them?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And how can anyone preach unless they are sent? As it is written: “How beautiful are the feet of those who bring good news!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28204V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28204V\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But not all the Israelites accepted the good news.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28205W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28205W\"></sup> For Isaiah says, “Lord, who has believed our message?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28205X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28205X\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Consequently, faith comes from hearing the message,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28206Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28206Y\"></sup> and the message is heard through the word about Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28206Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28206Z\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But I ask: Did they not hear? Of course they did:“Their voice has gone out into all the earth,their words to the ends of the world.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28207AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28207AA\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Again I ask: Did Israel not understand? First, Moses says,“I will make you envious<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28208AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28208AB\"></sup> by those who are not a nation;I will make you angry by a nation that has no understanding.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28208AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28208AC\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And Isaiah boldly says,“I was found by those who did not seek me;I revealed myself to those who did not ask for me.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28209AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28209AD\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But concerning Israel he says,“All day long I have held out my handsto a disobedient and obstinate people.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28210AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28210AE\"></sup>"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>I ask then: Did God reject his people? By no means!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28211A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28211A\"></sup> I am an Israelite myself, a descendant of Abraham,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28211B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28211B\"></sup> from the tribe of Benjamin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28211C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28211C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>God did not reject his people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28212D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28212D\"></sup> whom he foreknew.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28212E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28212E\"></sup> Don’t you know what Scripture says in the passage about Elijah—how he appealed to God against Israel:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Lord, they have killed your prophets and torn down your altars; I am the only one left, and they are trying to kill me”?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28213F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28213F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And what was God’s answer to him? “I have reserved for myself seven thousand who have not bowed the knee to Baal.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28214G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28214G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So too, at the present time there is a remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28215H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28215H\"></sup> chosen by grace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28215I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28215I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And if by grace, then it cannot be based on works;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28216J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28216J\"></sup> if it were, grace would no longer be grace.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>What then? What the people of Israel sought so earnestly they did not obtain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28217K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28217K\"></sup> The elect among them did, but the others were hardened,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28217L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28217L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>as it is written:“God gave them a spirit of stupor,eyes that could not seeand ears that could not hear,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28218M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28218M\"></sup>to this very day.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28218N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28218N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And David says:“May their table become a snare and a trap,a stumbling block and a retribution for them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>May their eyes be darkened so they cannot see,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28220O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28220O\"></sup>and their backs be bent forever.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28220P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28220P\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Again I ask: Did they stumble so as to fall beyond recovery? Not at all!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28221Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28221Q\"></sup> Rather, because of their transgression, salvation has come to the Gentiles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28221R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28221R\"></sup> to make Israel envious.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28221S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28221S\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But if their transgression means riches for the world, and their loss means riches for the Gentiles,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28222T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28222T\"></sup> how much greater riches will their full inclusion bring!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I am talking to you Gentiles. Inasmuch as I am the apostle to the Gentiles,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28223U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28223U\"></sup> I take pride in my ministry",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>in the hope that I may somehow arouse my own people to envy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28224V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28224V\"></sup> and save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28224W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28224W\"></sup> some of them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For if their rejection brought reconciliation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28225X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28225X\"></sup> to the world, what will their acceptance be but life from the dead?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28225Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28225Y\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>If the part of the dough offered as firstfruits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28226Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28226Z\"></sup> is holy, then the whole batch is holy; if the root is holy, so are the branches.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>If some of the branches have been broken off,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28227AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28227AA\"></sup> and you, though a wild olive shoot, have been grafted in among the others<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28227AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28227AB\"></sup> and now share in the nourishing sap from the olive root,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>do not consider yourself to be superior to those other branches. If you do, consider this: You do not support the root, but the root supports you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28228AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28228AC\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>You will say then, “Branches were broken off so that I could be grafted in.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Granted. But they were broken off because of unbelief, and you stand by faith.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28230AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28230AD\"></sup> Do not be arrogant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28230AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28230AE\"></sup> but tremble.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28230AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28230AF\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For if God did not spare the natural branches, he will not spare you either.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Consider therefore the kindness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28232AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28232AG\"></sup> and sternness of God: sternness to those who fell, but kindness to you, provided that you continue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28232AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28232AH\"></sup> in his kindness. Otherwise, you also will be cut off.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28232AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28232AI\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And if they do not persist in unbelief, they will be grafted in, for God is able to graft them in again.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28233AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28233AJ\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>After all, if you were cut out of an olive tree that is wild by nature, and contrary to nature were grafted into a cultivated olive tree,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28234AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28234AK\"></sup> how much more readily will these, the natural branches, be grafted into their own olive tree!",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I do not want you to be ignorant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28235AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28235AL\"></sup> of this mystery,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28235AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28235AM\"></sup> brothers and sisters, so that you may not be conceited:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28235AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28235AN\"></sup> Israel has experienced a hardening<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28235AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28235AO\"></sup> in part until the full number of the Gentiles has come in,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28235AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28235AP\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and in this way all Israel will be saved.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28236AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28236AQ\"></sup> As it is written:“The deliverer will come from Zion;he will turn godlessness away from Jacob.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And this is my covenant with themwhen I take away their sins.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28237AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28237AR\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>As far as the gospel is concerned, they are enemies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28238AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28238AS\"></sup> for your sake; but as far as election is concerned, they are loved on account of the patriarchs,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28238AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28238AT\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>for God’s gifts and his call<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28239AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28239AU\"></sup> are irrevocable.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28239AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28239AV\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Just as you who were at one time disobedient<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28240AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28240AW\"></sup> to God have now received mercy as a result of their disobedience,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>so they too have now become disobedient in order that they too may now receive mercy as a result of God’s mercy to you.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>For God has bound everyone over to disobedience<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28242AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28242AX\"></sup> so that he may have mercy on them all.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Oh, the depth of the riches<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28243AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28243AY\"></sup> of the wisdom and knowledge of God!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28243AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28243AZ\"></sup>How unsearchable his judgments,and his paths beyond tracing out!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28243BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28243BA\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“Who has known the mind of the Lord?Or who has been his counselor?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28244BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28244BB\"></sup>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“Who has ever given to God,that God should repay them?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28245BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28245BC\"></sup>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>For from him and through him and for him are all things.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28246BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28246BD\"></sup>To him be the glory forever! Amen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28246BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28246BE\"></sup>"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Therefore, I urge you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28247A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28247A\"></sup> brothers and sisters, in view of God’s mercy, to offer your bodies as a living sacrifice,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28247B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28247B\"></sup> holy and pleasing to God—this is your true and proper worship.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Do not conform<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28248C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28248C\"></sup> to the pattern of this world,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28248D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28248D\"></sup> but be transformed by the renewing of your mind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28248E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28248E\"></sup> Then you will be able to test and approve what God’s will is<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28248F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28248F\"></sup>—his good, pleasing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28248G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28248G\"></sup> and perfect will.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For by the grace given me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28249H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28249H\"></sup> I say to every one of you: Do not think of yourself more highly than you ought, but rather think of yourself with sober judgment, in accordance with the faith God has distributed to each of you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For just as each of us has one body with many members, and these members do not all have the same function,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28250I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28250I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>so in Christ we, though many, form one body,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28251J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28251J\"></sup> and each member belongs to all the others.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>We have different gifts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28252K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28252K\"></sup> according to the grace given to each of us. If your gift is prophesying,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28252L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28252L\"></sup> then prophesy in accordance with your faith;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28252M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28252M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>if it is serving, then serve; if it is teaching, then teach;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28253N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28253N\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>if it is to encourage, then give encouragement;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28254O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28254O\"></sup> if it is giving, then give generously;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28254P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28254P\"></sup> if it is to lead, do it diligently; if it is to show mercy, do it cheerfully.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Love must be sincere.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28255Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28255Q\"></sup> Hate what is evil; cling to what is good.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28255R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28255R\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Be devoted to one another in love.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28256S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28256S\"></sup> Honor one another above yourselves.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28256T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28256T\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Never be lacking in zeal, but keep your spiritual fervor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28257U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28257U\"></sup> serving the Lord.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Be joyful in hope,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28258V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28258V\"></sup> patient in affliction,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28258W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28258W\"></sup> faithful in prayer.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28258X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28258X\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Share with the Lord’s people who are in need.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28259Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28259Y\"></sup> Practice hospitality.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28259Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28259Z\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Bless those who persecute you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28260AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28260AA\"></sup> bless and do not curse.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Rejoice with those who rejoice; mourn with those who mourn.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28261AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28261AB\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Live in harmony with one another.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28262AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28262AC\"></sup> Do not be proud, but be willing to associate with people of low position. Do not be conceited.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28262AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28262AD\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Do not repay anyone evil for evil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28263AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28263AE\"></sup> Be careful to do what is right in the eyes of everyone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28263AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28263AF\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>If it is possible, as far as it depends on you, live at peace with everyone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28264AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28264AG\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Do not take revenge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28265AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28265AH\"></sup> my dear friends, but leave room for God’s wrath, for it is written: “It is mine to avenge; I will repay,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28265AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28265AI\"></sup> says the Lord.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>On the contrary:“If your enemy is hungry, feed him;if he is thirsty, give him something to drink.In doing this, you will heap burning coals on his head.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28266AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28266AJ\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Do not be overcome by evil, but overcome evil with good."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>Let everyone be subject to the governing authorities,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28268A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28268A\"></sup> for there is no authority except that which God has established.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28268B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28268B\"></sup> The authorities that exist have been established by God.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Consequently, whoever rebels against the authority is rebelling against what God has instituted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28269C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28269C\"></sup> and those who do so will bring judgment on themselves.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For rulers hold no terror for those who do right, but for those who do wrong. Do you want to be free from fear of the one in authority? Then do what is right and you will be commended.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28270D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28270D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For the one in authority is God’s servant for your good. But if you do wrong, be afraid, for rulers do not bear the sword for no reason. They are God’s servants, agents of wrath to bring punishment on the wrongdoer.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28271E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28271E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Therefore, it is necessary to submit to the authorities, not only because of possible punishment but also as a matter of conscience.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28272F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28272F\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>This is also why you pay taxes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28273G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28273G\"></sup> for the authorities are God’s servants, who give their full time to governing.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Give to everyone what you owe them: If you owe taxes, pay taxes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28274H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28274H\"></sup> if revenue, then revenue; if respect, then respect; if honor, then honor.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Let no debt remain outstanding, except the continuing debt to love one another, for whoever loves others has fulfilled the law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28275I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28275I\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The commandments, “You shall not commit adultery,” “You shall not murder,” “You shall not steal,” “You shall not covet,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28276J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28276J\"></sup> and whatever other command there may be, are summed up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28276K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28276K\"></sup> in this one command: “Love your neighbor as yourself.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28276L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28276L\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Love does no harm to a neighbor. Therefore love is the fulfillment of the law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28277M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28277M\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And do this, understanding the present time: The hour has already come<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28278N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28278N\"></sup> for you to wake up from your slumber,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28278O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28278O\"></sup> because our salvation is nearer now than when we first believed.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The night is nearly over; the day is almost here.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28279P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28279P\"></sup> So let us put aside the deeds of darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28279Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28279Q\"></sup> and put on the armor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28279R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28279R\"></sup> of light.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Let us behave decently, as in the daytime, not in carousing and drunkenness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28280S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28280S\"></sup> not in sexual immorality and debauchery, not in dissension and jealousy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28280T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28280T\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Rather, clothe yourselves with the Lord Jesus Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28281U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28281U\"></sup> and do not think about how to gratify the desires of the flesh.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28281V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28281V\"></sup>"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>Accept the one whose faith is weak,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28282A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28282A\"></sup> without quarreling over disputable matters.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>One person’s faith allows them to eat anything, but another, whose faith is weak, eats only vegetables.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28283B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28283B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The one who eats everything must not treat with contempt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28284C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28284C\"></sup> the one who does not, and the one who does not eat everything must not judge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28284D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28284D\"></sup> the one who does, for God has accepted them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Who are you to judge someone else’s servant?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28285E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28285E\"></sup> To their own master, servants stand or fall. And they will stand, for the Lord is able to make them stand.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>One person considers one day more sacred than another;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28286F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28286F\"></sup> another considers every day alike. Each of them should be fully convinced in their own mind.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Whoever regards one day as special does so to the Lord. Whoever eats meat does so to the Lord, for they give thanks to God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28287G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28287G\"></sup> and whoever abstains does so to the Lord and gives thanks to God.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For none of us lives for ourselves alone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28288H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28288H\"></sup> and none of us dies for ourselves alone.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>If we live, we live for the Lord; and if we die, we die for the Lord. So, whether we live or die, we belong to the Lord.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28289I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28289I\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For this very reason, Christ died and returned to life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28290J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28290J\"></sup> so that he might be the Lord of both the dead and the living.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28290K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28290K\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>You, then, why do you judge your brother or sister? Or why do you treat them with contempt?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28291L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28291L\"></sup> For we will all stand before God’s judgment seat.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28291M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28291M\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>It is written:“‘As surely as I live,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28292N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28292N\"></sup> says the Lord,‘every knee will bow before me;every tongue will acknowledge God.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28292O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28292O\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So then, each of us will give an account of ourselves to God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28293P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28293P\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore let us stop passing judgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28294Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28294Q\"></sup> on one another. Instead, make up your mind not to put any stumbling block or obstacle in the way of a brother or sister.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28294R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28294R\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I am convinced, being fully persuaded in the Lord Jesus, that nothing is unclean in itself.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28295S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28295S\"></sup> But if anyone regards something as unclean, then for that person it is unclean.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28295T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28295T\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>If your brother or sister is distressed because of what you eat, you are no longer acting in love.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28296U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28296U\"></sup> Do not by your eating destroy someone for whom Christ died.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28296V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28296V\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore do not let what you know is good be spoken of as evil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28297W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28297W\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For the kingdom of God is not a matter of eating and drinking,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28298X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28298X\"></sup> but of righteousness, peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28298Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28298Y\"></sup> and joy in the Holy Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28298Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28298Z\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>because anyone who serves Christ in this way is pleasing to God and receives human approval.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28299AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28299AA\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Let us therefore make every effort to do what leads to peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28300AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28300AB\"></sup> and to mutual edification.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28300AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28300AC\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Do not destroy the work of God for the sake of food.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28301AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28301AD\"></sup> All food is clean,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28301AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28301AE\"></sup> but it is wrong for a person to eat anything that causes someone else to stumble.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28301AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28301AF\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>It is better not to eat meat or drink wine or to do anything else that will cause your brother or sister to fall.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28302AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28302AG\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So whatever you believe about these things keep between yourself and God. Blessed is the one who does not condemn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28303AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28303AH\"></sup> himself by what he approves.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But whoever has doubts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28304AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28304AI\"></sup> is condemned if they eat, because their eating is not from faith; and everything that does not come from faith is sin."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>We who are strong ought to bear with the failings of the weak<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28305A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28305A\"></sup> and not to please ourselves.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Each of us should please our neighbors for their good,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28306B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28306B\"></sup> to build them up.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28306C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28306C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For even Christ did not please himself<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28307D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28307D\"></sup> but, as it is written: “The insults of those who insult you have fallen on me.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28307E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28307E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For everything that was written in the past was written to teach us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28308F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28308F\"></sup> so that through the endurance taught in the Scriptures and the encouragement they provide we might have hope.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>May the God who gives endurance and encouragement give you the same attitude of mind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28309G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28309G\"></sup> toward each other that Christ Jesus had,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>so that with one mind and one voice you may glorify<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28310H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28310H\"></sup> the God and Father<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28310I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28310I\"></sup> of our Lord Jesus Christ.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Accept one another,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28311J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28311J\"></sup> then, just as Christ accepted you, in order to bring praise to God.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For I tell you that Christ has become a servant of the Jews<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28312K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28312K\"></sup> on behalf of God’s truth, so that the promises<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28312L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28312L\"></sup> made to the patriarchs might be confirmed",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and, moreover, that the Gentiles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28313M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28313M\"></sup> might glorify God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28313N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28313N\"></sup> for his mercy. As it is written:“Therefore I will praise you among the Gentiles;I will sing the praises of your name.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28313O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28313O\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Again, it says,“Rejoice, you Gentiles, with his people.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28314P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28314P\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And again,“Praise the Lord, all you Gentiles;let all the peoples extol him.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28315Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28315Q\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And again, Isaiah says,“The Root of Jesse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28316R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28316R\"></sup> will spring up,one who will arise to rule over the nations;in him the Gentiles will hope.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28316S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28316S\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>May the God of hope fill you with all joy and peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28317T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28317T\"></sup> as you trust in him, so that you may overflow with hope by the power of the Holy Spirit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28317U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28317U\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I myself am convinced, my brothers and sisters, that you yourselves are full of goodness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28318V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28318V\"></sup> filled with knowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28318W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28318W\"></sup> and competent to instruct one another.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Yet I have written you quite boldly on some points to remind you of them again, because of the grace God gave me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28319X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28319X\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>to be a minister of Christ Jesus to the Gentiles.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28320Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28320Y\"></sup> He gave me the priestly duty of proclaiming the gospel of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28320Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28320Z\"></sup> so that the Gentiles might become an offering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28320AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28320AA\"></sup> acceptable to God, sanctified by the Holy Spirit.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Therefore I glory in Christ Jesus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28321AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28321AB\"></sup> in my service to God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28321AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28321AC\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I will not venture to speak of anything except what Christ has accomplished through me in leading the Gentiles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28322AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28322AD\"></sup> to obey God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28322AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28322AE\"></sup> by what I have said and done—",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>by the power of signs and wonders,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28323AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28323AF\"></sup> through the power of the Spirit of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28323AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28323AG\"></sup> So from Jerusalem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28323AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28323AH\"></sup> all the way around to Illyricum, I have fully proclaimed the gospel of Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28323AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28323AI\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>It has always been my ambition to preach the gospel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28324AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28324AJ\"></sup> where Christ was not known, so that I would not be building on someone else’s foundation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28324AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28324AK\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Rather, as it is written:“Those who were not told about him will see,and those who have not heard will understand.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28325AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28325AL\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>This is why I have often been hindered from coming to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28326AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28326AM\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But now that there is no more place for me to work in these regions, and since I have been longing for many years to visit you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28327AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28327AN\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>I plan to do so when I go to Spain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28328AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28328AO\"></sup> I hope to see you while passing through and to have you assist<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28328AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28328AP\"></sup> me on my journey there, after I have enjoyed your company for a while.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Now, however, I am on my way to Jerusalem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28329AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28329AQ\"></sup> in the service<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28329AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28329AR\"></sup> of the Lord’s people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28329AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28329AS\"></sup> there.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For Macedonia<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28330AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28330AT\"></sup> and Achaia<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28330AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28330AU\"></sup> were pleased to make a contribution for the poor among the Lord’s people in Jerusalem.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28330AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28330AV\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>They were pleased to do it, and indeed they owe it to them. For if the Gentiles have shared in the Jews’ spiritual blessings, they owe it to the Jews to share with them their material blessings.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28331AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28331AW\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So after I have completed this task and have made sure that they have received this contribution, I will go to Spain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28332AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28332AX\"></sup> and visit you on the way.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>I know that when I come to you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28333AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28333AY\"></sup> I will come in the full measure of the blessing of Christ.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>I urge you, brothers and sisters, by our Lord Jesus Christ and by the love of the Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28334AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28334AZ\"></sup> to join me in my struggle by praying to God for me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28334BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28334BA\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Pray that I may be kept safe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28335BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28335BB\"></sup> from the unbelievers in Judea and that the contribution<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28335BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28335BC\"></sup> I take to Jerusalem may be favorably received by the Lord’s people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28335BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28335BD\"></sup> there,",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>so that I may come to you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28336BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28336BE\"></sup> with joy, by God’s will,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28336BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28336BF\"></sup> and in your company be refreshed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28336BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28336BG\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>The God of peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28337BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28337BH\"></sup> be with you all. Amen."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>I commend<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28338A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28338A\"></sup> to you our sister Phoebe, a deacon of the church in Cenchreae.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28338B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28338B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I ask you to receive her in the Lord<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28339C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28339C\"></sup> in a way worthy of his people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28339D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28339D\"></sup> and to give her any help she may need from you, for she has been the benefactor of many people, including me.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Greet Priscilla and Aquila,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28340E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28340E\"></sup> my co-workers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28340F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28340F\"></sup> in Christ Jesus.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28340G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28340G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They risked their lives for me. Not only I but all the churches of the Gentiles are grateful to them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Greet also the church that meets at their house.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28342H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28342H\"></sup>Greet my dear friend Epenetus, who was the first convert<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28342I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28342I\"></sup> to Christ in the province of Asia.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28342J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28342J\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Greet Mary, who worked very hard for you.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Greet Andronicus and Junia, my fellow Jews<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28344K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28344K\"></sup> who have been in prison with me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28344L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28344L\"></sup> They are outstanding among the apostles, and they were in Christ<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28344M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28344M\"></sup> before I was.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Greet Ampliatus, my dear friend in the Lord.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Greet Urbanus, our co-worker in Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28346N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28346N\"></sup> and my dear friend Stachys.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Greet Apelles, whose fidelity to Christ has stood the test.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28347O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28347O\"></sup>Greet those who belong to the household<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28347P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28347P\"></sup> of Aristobulus.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Greet Herodion, my fellow Jew.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28348Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28348Q\"></sup>Greet those in the household<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28348R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28348R\"></sup> of Narcissus who are in the Lord.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Greet Tryphena and Tryphosa, those women who work hard in the Lord.Greet my dear friend Persis, another woman who has worked very hard in the Lord.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Greet Rufus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28350S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28350S\"></sup> chosen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28350T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28350T\"></sup> in the Lord, and his mother, who has been a mother to me, too.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Greet Asyncritus, Phlegon, Hermes, Patrobas, Hermas and the other brothers and sisters with them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Greet Philologus, Julia, Nereus and his sister, and Olympas and all the Lord’s people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28352U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28352U\"></sup> who are with them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28352V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28352V\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Greet one another with a holy kiss.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28353W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28353W\"></sup>All the churches of Christ send greetings.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I urge you, brothers and sisters, to watch out for those who cause divisions and put obstacles in your way that are contrary to the teaching you have learned.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28354X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28354X\"></sup> Keep away from them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28354Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28354Y\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For such people are not serving our Lord Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28355Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28355Z\"></sup> but their own appetites.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28355AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28355AA\"></sup> By smooth talk and flattery they deceive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28355AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28355AB\"></sup> the minds of naive people.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Everyone has heard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28356AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28356AC\"></sup> about your obedience, so I rejoice because of you; but I want you to be wise about what is good, and innocent about what is evil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28356AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28356AD\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The God of peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28357AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28357AE\"></sup> will soon crush<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28357AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28357AF\"></sup> Satan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28357AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28357AG\"></sup> under your feet.The grace of our Lord Jesus be with you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28357AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28357AH\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Timothy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28358AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28358AI\"></sup> my co-worker, sends his greetings to you, as do Lucius,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28358AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28358AJ\"></sup> Jason<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28358AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28358AK\"></sup> and Sosipater, my fellow Jews.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28358AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28358AL\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>I, Tertius, who wrote down this letter, greet you in the Lord.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Gaius,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28360AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28360AM\"></sup> whose hospitality I and the whole church here enjoy, sends you his greetings.Erastus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28360AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28360AN\"></sup> who is the city’s director of public works, and our brother Quartus send you their greetings.<sup class=\"versenum\">[24] </sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Now to him who is able<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28362AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28362AO\"></sup> to establish you in accordance with my gospel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28362AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28362AP\"></sup> the message I proclaim about Jesus Christ, in keeping with the revelation of the mystery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28362AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28362AQ\"></sup> hidden for long ages past,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>but now revealed and made known through the prophetic writings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28363AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28363AR\"></sup> by the command of the eternal God, so that all the Gentiles might come to the obedience that comes from faith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28363AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28363AS\"></sup>—",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>to the only wise God be glory forever through Jesus Christ! Amen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28364AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28364AT\"></sup>"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;